JDBC Key , Git key based key , Git password based key, Terminal key with RCA SSH key with passphrase and sudo admin password(16385 bytes key), Terminal Key with ed25519 SSH encription  no passphrase, Email , Windows and AWS

JDBC , Git Endpoint target based on key-based , Git Endpoint target based on password-based, Git Repo target based on key-based , Git Repo target based on password based , Terminal Target based on RSA, Terminal Target based on ed25519, Linux Target based on RSA , Linux Target based on ed25519 ,
IMAP target, POP3 target, SMTP target , Windows Target and AWS target

Delete all created target and keys if it is requried ( by default Delete local variable seet to true)

Try to modify key and target with invalid data while valid key and target already created
